\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 The transistor is like a bicycle gear: you control it with a small amount of current, and it in turn can control a lot more current.\
The transistor also allows us to use a higher voltage than the 5V Arduino can deliver.\
